阅历，但普通人的奋斗故事同样能收获大量粉丝。用诚信、真诚赢得的关注和粉丝，远比虚构人设来得更牢靠。千万网红被指学历造假，诚信比人设更重要"},"attached_info":"CkAIu7HWparfwdF4EAMaCTExMTE1ODcyOSCP07a4BjAAOPMFQBpyCTkyMTA1ODIzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"39 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dfea286a2a5506f0c550fa9a79381461_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1729049272.109768","card_id":"Q_667247080","target":{"id":667247080,"title":"唐尚珺为什么不继续复读了？感觉他毕业后也不好找工作啊？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/667247080","type":"question","created":1726394554,"answer_count":127,"follower_count":316,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[40115,199568,1357440,2827780],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"不是应该继续高考，然后直播收大家打赏吗？"},"attached_info":"CkAIu7HWparfwdF4EAMaCTExMDU1NDc3MyC64Zq3BjAAOLwCQBtyCTY2NzI0NzA4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3674f635dbf72685e760ad40f5495f1c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1729049272.110227","card_id":"Q_287526924","target":{"id":287526924,"title":"如果你是《西虹市首富》男主角，你将怎么样在一个月内花光十亿？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/287526924","type":"question","created":1532882298,"answer_count":3034,"follower_count":4980,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,3489,6142,88888,220628],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"条件和电影中的条件一样。 1.不能做违反中国大陆法律法规的事情（包括所有的黄赌毒行为）。 2.不能雇佣或者保有超过100名员工。并且所有员工的薪酬不能超过市场最高价。 3.一个月后不能有剩余的固定资产。 4.不能做慈善事业，不能赠予给他人金钱和物品 5.不能故意毁坏财物。 6.所有的资金必须运用到自己身上（应该电影里的条件）。 7.不能让其他人知道这一赌注。 希望各位知友能大开脑洞，题主本人见识短浅，看这部电影时候只想到请明星开私人演唱会这一手法。顺带通过这个题来了解一下什么东西烧钱到难以想象（PS：好像知道了也没用）"},"attached_